        "difficulty": "extremely_difficult",
        "title": "Diagnose hidden shared-state mutation in a 'pure' helper",
        "intent": (
            "Run `python -m unittest -q`. One test fails non-deterministically — "
            "actually it fails reproducibly here, but it LOOKS like flakiness. "
            "Do not edit any file. Identify the exact file and function whose "
